different biochemistry.

01:08:03.289 --> 01:08:04.830
But I want to go a
little bit further

01:08:04.830 --> 01:08:08.170
into that is if you look
at oxygenic photosynthesis.

01:08:08.170 --> 01:08:11.880
It relies on CO2 and
water and starlight.

01:08:11.880 --> 01:08:14.360
Those things are going to be
on other planets, you know,

01:08:14.360 --> 01:08:16.189
because those are both common.

01:08:16.189 --> 01:08:21.149
