able to take advantage of it,

01:08:25.060 --> 01:08:25.560
it would.

01:08:25.560 --> 01:08:29.340
Because you have a lot of
energy source from the star,

01:08:29.340 --> 01:08:31.760
and then you're using
things that we know

01:08:31.760 --> 01:08:34.229
are common on other planets.

01:08:34.229 --> 01:08:36.819
So that might lead
rise to oxygen.

01:08:36.819 --> 01:08:40.399
And then on the flip side of for
why oxygen is important for us,

01:08:40.399 --> 01:08:42.819
you get twice the
amount of redox energy

01:08:42.819 --> 01:08:48.340
from oxygen, about, as from
the next chemical gradient.

01:08:48.340 --> 01:08:54.140
So this is what led to the
rise of complex life on Earth.

